analysis.description: This modern kitchen in a South Indian style features white countertops, glass cabinets, and a wooden dining table. The space includes a decorative Ganesha idol, symbolizing cultural significance. The staircase with glass railings adds a contemporary touch, while the overall design incorporates traditional Indian elements in its decor and materials. The lighting is bright and evenly distributed, and the countertops have a shiny polished finish, enhancing the modern aesthetic of the kitchen.

metadata.budget_indicator: High, due to polished materials and contemporary design
